snippet: American Christina McHale beat Japan's Misaki Doi 6-2 4-6 7-5 at the Miami Open on Wednesday to set up a second-round showdown with defending champion and world number one Serena Williams....
lead_paragraph: American Christina McHale beat Japan's Misaki Doi 6-2 4-6 7-5 at the Miami Open on Wednesday to set up a second-round showdown with defending champion and world number one Serena Williams.

headline.print_headline: McHale Edges Doi, Sets Up Miami Showdown With Serena
headline.main: McHale Edges Doi, Sets Up Miami Showdown With Serena
